          <h2>About Us</h2>
          <p id='aboutP'> This service is not a publisher! We are here to help you prepare your work for self-publishing 
              or to submit it to publishers.
              <br>
              <br>
              ​Authors are usually faced with two options, and neither are very good. On the one hand, there 
              are platforms that let you quickly distribute your book, but do nothing to help your book be 
              publishing-ready or to stand out from the crowd.
              <br>
              <br>
              On the other hand, there are self-publishing services that sell exorbitant package deals, 
              with vague promises of what they are delivering and mystery surrounding their high costs.
              <br>
              <br>
              For an author new to publishing, it can be confusing concerning what's needed and what's not. 
              As a team experienced with the publishing world, we provide a suite of services that give 
              authors exactly what they need.
              <br>
              <br>
              Publishing Assist was created to give you the ability to be independent without truly having 
              to go it alone. Now you can buy competitively priced publishing services for your books as you 
              want them, à la carte.
              <br>
              <br>
              Publishing Assist was created by Brian Quezada, a founder of MQuills Publishing. Brian and his 
              team have 9 years experience in independent publishing, and have helped authors around the world 
              to get their books in front of readers.
          </p>
